security_findings.evidence:
UNPATCHED AfdSanFastCompleteRequest — IRP linked into list under the endpoint spinlock:
```c
// endpoint spinlock [endpoint+0x30] already held
*(Irp + 0x68) = AfdSanCancelRequest;      // set cancel routine
if (!*(Irp + 0x44))                        // IRP->Cancel
{
    void* head = *(Endpoint + 0x70);       // endpoint IRP list head
    *(Irp + 0xa8) = head;                   // link IRP into endpoint list (under lock)
    ...
}
```

PATCHED AfdSanFastCompleteRequest — added feature-gated abort-state check, same lock:
```c
*(Irp + 0x68) = AfdSanCancelRequest;
if (!*(Irp + 0x44)
    && (!EvaluateCurrentState(&g_Feature_757798200_60363861_FeatureDescriptorDetails)
        || !*(Endpoint + 0x91)))           // feature off OR endpoint not aborting
{
    void* head = *(Endpoint + 0x70);
    *(Irp + 0xa8) = head;                   // otherwise complete IRP STATUS_CANCELLED
    ...
}
```

UNPATCHED AfdSanRedirectRequest — IRP linked into list under the endpoint spinlock, no abort-byte check:
```c
// endpoint spinlock [endpoint+0x30] held throughout
arg1->CancelRoutine = AfdSanCancelRequest;
if (!arg1->Cancel)                 // IRP->Cancel
{
    // link IRP into endpoint list at [endpoint+0x70]
    ...
}
```

PATCHED AfdSanRedirectRequest — feature-gated abort-byte check added, same lock:
```c
arg1->CancelRoutine = AfdSanCancelRequest;
if (!arg1->Cancel
    && (!EvaluateCurrentState(&g_Feature_757798200_60363861_FeatureDescriptorDetails)
        || !*(Endpoint + 0x91)))   // feature off OR endpoint not aborting
{
    // otherwise complete IRP STATUS_CANCELLED
    ...
}
```
